âœ… Interview ke liye PERFECT answer ğŸ†

ğŸ‘‰ Agar interviewer poochay:

â“ REST API kya hoti hai?

Best answer:

REST API frontend aur backend ke beech communication ka tareeqa hoti hai jisme hum HTTP methods jaise GET, POST, PUT, DELETE ka use karke data ko create, read, update aur delete karte hain.

â“ Express.js mein REST API kaise banate ho?

Best answer:

Express.js mein hum routes banate hain jaise app.get, app.post, app.put aur app.delete.
Har route ek specific HTTP request handle karta hai aur JSON response return karta hai.


