ğŸ”¹ Interview ke liye ready-made answer ğŸ§ âœ¨

ğŸ‘‰ Q: REST API kya hoti hai?

REST API ek architectural style hai jo client aur server ke beech communication ke liye use hoti hai.
Ye HTTP methods (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE) ke through CRUD operations perform karti hai.

ğŸ‘‰ Q: Express.js mein REST API kaise banate ho?

Express.js mein hum routes create kartay hain jahan different HTTP methods use hotay hain.
Har route ek specific task perform karta hai jaise data fetch, create, update ya delete.

